title: Grid for St. Georg (n=570)
name: Grid for St. Georg (n=570)
description:
This dataset only includes the intersections of a grid laid out over St. Georg (Hamburg, Germany) from 
latitude 53.549 to 53.566 North and 
longitude 9.998 to 10.027 East. 

Intersections are named A1 to S30 with a total n of 570 (=19*30).

author.source: This data was created by myself.
